Xakamaynta halista shaqada ee COVID-19 waxaa loola jeedaa in la hirgeliyo hababka caafimaadka iyo badbaadada ee shaqada si loo xakameeyo halista iyo ka hortagga bilowga coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
