Waxaa la ogaaday in ACE2 ee loo yaqaan 'human neutreceptor receptor receptor receptor receptor 2' (rhACE2) uu yahay daaweyn cusub oo loogu talagalay dhaawaca sanbabada ee daran, wuxuuna horseeday hagaajinta hemodynamics sanbabada iyo cusbooneysiinta oksijiinta ee doofaarka qaba cudurka 'acute pulmonary dysteresis syndrome' oo ay sababtay lipopolysaccharide.
Nolosha badhtamaha ee rhACE2 ee aadanaha waa qiyaastii 10 saacadood, bilowga waxqabadka 30 daqiiqo iyo muddo 24 saac ah.
Cilmi baaris kala duwan ayaa muujineysa in rhACE2 ay noqon karto daawo rajo leh oo loogu talagalay dadka u adkaysta xakameeyayaasha nidaamka rennin-angiotensin (RAS inhibitors) ama bukaannada qaba xakameynta muddada dheer ee angiotensin II. Cirbadeynta rhACE2 ayaa lagu baaray daraasado caafimaad oo lagu daaweynayo cudurka 'acute respiratory dysteresis syndrome'.
