Ross Anderson, oo ah borofisar ku takhasusay injineernimada amniga ee Jaamacadda Cambridge, ayaa ku taxay dhibaatooyin badan oo ku saabsan nidaamyada barnaamijka ku saleysan, oo ay ku jiraan kiisaska been abuurka ah iyo waxtar la'aanta haddii barnaamijka loo isticmaalo qaybo yar oo dadka ah.
